===Etymology 1===
From {{etyl|enm}}, from {{etyl|ang}} {{term|hwy|hwȳ|lang=ang}}, {{term|hwi|hwī|why|lit=by what, for what||pos=instrumental case of {{term|hwæt||what|lang=ang}}|lang=ang}}, from {{etyl|gem-pro|en}} {{recons|hwī||by what, how|lang=gem-pro}}, from {{etyl|ine-pro|en}} {{recons|kʷey|lang=ine-pro}}, locative of {{recons|kʷís||who|lang=ine-pro}}. Cognate with {{etyl|gmh|-}} {{term|wiu||how, why|lang=gmh}}, {{etyl|da|-}} and {{etyl|sv|-}} {{term|hvi||why|lang=da|lang=sv}}, {{etyl|fo|-}} and {{etyl|is|-}} {{term|hví||why|lang=fo|lang=is}}, {{etyl|la|-}} {{term|cui||to whom|pos=dative case of {{term|qui|quī|who, how, why|lang=la}}|lang=la}}, {{etyl|grc|-}} {{term|πει||tr=pei|where|lang=grc}}. Compare {{etyl|ang|-}} {{term|þy|þȳ|because, since, on that account, therefore, then|lit=by that, for that|lang=ang}}. See {{l|en|thy}}.

